 \[ y =   $a x \cos x  \]
at the point \( ( \pi , $m \pi) \).
$BR $BR
The equation of this tangent line can be written in the form \( y = mx+b \) where
$BR $BR
\( m = \) \{ans_rule(20) \}
$BR $BR
and \( b = \) \{ans_rule(20) \}
END_TEXT

ANS($m->cmp);

